				<wikidot:authorName>DarkStuff</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1581620</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>That’s a great idea, honestly that’s super creative. However, the containment needs to not be perfect, ‘cause he escapes, and&#8230; well, I headcanon that they don’t write down further containment attempts, to try and subvert their being a written narrative which would dampen his anomaly (methinks). And I just don’t think there’s room in this article to really describe Expositor, especially since he’s a neutralised anomaly that they never got to study.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
